		"description": "<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"988a4f6c-c2e3-476b-bc81-14bca562aed3\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o\">\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">At 9th level, you are granted a distinction from an important scientific group, political faction, or military force. Roll [[/r 3d6]], choose, or work with the Narrator to determine the origin and nature of this distinction. As a recipient of that prize, your Prestige score increases by 1, and you gain 1,000 credits.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Furthermore, choose a skill related to this achievement. You gain proficiency in that skill and an expertise die on checks made with it. For you, expertise dice in the chosen skill can be upgraded to d12, exceeding the usual limit on expertise dice.</p>\n<hr>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 11.3429%;\">Roll</th>\n<th style=\"width: 88.5919%;\">Faction</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 11.3429%;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left; width: 88.5919%;\">The Fleet</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 11.3429%;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left; width: 88.5919%;\">Scientific research organization</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 11.3429%;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left; width: 88.5919%;\">Famous charity</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 11.3429%;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left; width: 88.5919%;\">Social media icon or news outlet</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 11.3429%;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left; width: 88.5919%;\">Religious organization</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 11.3429%;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left; width: 88.5919%;\">Criminal organization</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Roll</th>\n<th>Achievement</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Physics or Chemistry</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Biology or Medicine</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Information Technology or Cybernetics</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Peacemaking or Social Justice</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Courage or Public Service</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">“Person of the Year”</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Roll</th>\n<th>Prize</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<td>1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Trophy of gold, platinum, or other precious substance</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<td>2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Medal, insignia, or ribbon</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<td>3</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Portrait, bust, or statue</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<td>4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">University or hospital wing named after you</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<td>5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Honorary doctoral degree</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Honorary title of nobility</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-2 flex gap-3 empty:hidden -ml-2\">\n<div class=\"items-center justify-start rounded-xl p-1 flex\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
